            Projects can be shared among multiple users, facilitating team collaboration and progress tracking.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white">
            </div>
